node.text: Denzel with the big play on 3rd and long 😤😤 #NYGvsNYJ #Jets #Giants #Preseason

Zach Wilson’s night is done, Mike White in at QB. The rookie finishes his debut 6/9 for 63 yards, leading the team on one scoring drive (field goal). 

What were your thoughts on his performance? 🤔 #Jets #Giants #ZachWilson

node.text: The Jets have finally decided to add a veteran to their QB room, agreeing to terms with Josh Johnson. The 2008 5th round pick had a brief stint in New York during the 2015 offseason. The team also waived LB Brendon White. #Jets #JoshJohnson
